	* pytis/presentation/spec.py (Specification._create_data_spec):
	Added assertion to disable setting `access_rights' for a `MemData'
	data object.

	* ChangeLog.3: New file.

	* ChangeLog: Records prior to 2006-12-13 saved to `ChangeLog.3'.

